      "writtenOn": "2026-05-28T16:58:53Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "[Critical] Line 80: The `showOriginal` state is stored on the reusable delegate and is not reset when the delegate is rebound to another message. If a delegate that previously displayed a plugin-overwritten message is reused for a normal edited message, this branch can execute with `isPluginOverwrite \u003d\u003d false` and access `PreviousBodies[0].body`, which may be undefined and can also display the wrong message body. Reset `showOriginal` when the message identity changes and avoid the unused non-plugin fallback. Suggested fix:\\n```suggestion\\nonIdChanged: showOriginal \u003d false\\n\\ntext: {\\n    if (showOriginal \u0026\u0026 isPluginOverwrite)\\n        return OriginalBody;\\n```",
      "revId": "8820437952e4bbe13e0806b53ee99bf514ee70cc",
      "serverId": "1e26b4c1-6b8c-47ff-9df7-501b633d3b5a"
    },
